title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA -  Old Faithful Inn
description:
In this video we will fly over the Old Faithful Inn. The Old Faithful Inn is a hotel in the western United States with a view of the Old Faithful Geyser, located in Yellowstone National Park, Wyoming. The Inn has a multi-story log lobby, flanked by long frame wings containing guest rooms. In the western portion of the park, it sits at an approximate elevation of 7,350 feet (2,240 m) above sea level.
